\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Plus some small materials (examples, riddles, etcetera) that I do during
 the lectures
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Almost nothing is posted on the web
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
We are using R for software
